data.description: Enjoy nature at its best!  DO NOT WALK PROPERTY WITHOUT APPOINTMENT.  AMAZING & UNIQUE 14.99 acre parcel nestled in nature with two beautiful ponds and a plethora of wildlife for ONLY $185,000 ....That is $12,333 per acre PLUS IMPROVEMENTS and a mobile home!!! 2002 FIXER UPPER 2/2 Redman Manufactured home with 1296 living included however primary value in the land, impact fees & improvements.  So many possibilities for this hidden gem.  Location provides easy access to Citrus, Levy and Marion Counties.
